data.description: INCREDIBLE INCOME PRODUCING PROPERTY or perfect for an end user! Step inside this 1,924 sq ft Spanish style home offering 3 beds + den and 2 full baths! The layout of this home offers split bedrooms for privacy and private entrance in one of the bedrooms. This home features a commercial grade roof designed to last! The kitchen features modern black cabinets with a glossy finish, stainless steel appliances and Butcher Block countertops! Stay cool in the hot summer months with a FOUR TON A/C unit, water heater, washer and dryer and plenty of parking! Lush and expansive back yard with plenty of room for a pool or to build another unit! It also features a MASSIVE shed for additional storage!     Perfect for short term rentals with NO RESTRICTIONS! Minutes to Wynwood, Brickell & MIA Airport!!!
